-teatro-socialetosca/?format=pdf" title="Download PDF"><img alt="Download PDF" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/plugins/wp-post-to-pdf/asset/images/pdf.png"></a></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="entry-extra clearfix"><div class="comments-link " style="color: #363636"> <i class="icon-comment"></i> <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/10/rovigo-teatro-socialetosca/#respond"><span class="leave-reply" style="color:#363636 !important;">Leave a reply</span></a></div><div class="entry-share"> <span style="color: #363636">Share This<i class="icon-plus"></i></span><div class="entry-share-icons"> <span class="ct-pinterest" title="Share on Pinterest"><a href="http://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=http://www.gbopera.it/2013/10/rovigo-teatro-socialetosca/&amp;media=http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/tosca8-1024x682.jpg&amp;description=Rovigo,%20Teatro%20Sociale:&#8221;Tosca&#8221;" target="_blank"><i class="icon-pinterest"></i></a></span> <span class="ct-fb" title="Share on Facebook"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=http://www.gbopera.it/2013/10/rovigo-teatro-socialetosca/" target="_blank"><i class="icon-facebook"></i></a></span> <span class="ct-twitter" title="Share on Twitter"><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Rovigo,%20Teatro%20Sociale:&#8221;Tosca&#8221;&amp;url=http://www.gbopera.it/2013/10/rovigo-teatro-socialetosca/" target="_blank"><i class="icon-twitter"></i></a></span> <span class="ct-gplus" title="Share on Google Plus"><a href="https://plus.google.com/share?url=http://www.gbopera.it/2013/10/rovigo-teatro-socialetosca/" target="_blank"><i class="icon-google-plus"></i></a></span></div></div></div><footer class="entry-meta single-meta clearfix"><div class="entry-date updated"> <span class="date-month">Ott</span> <span class="date-day">19</span><meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Ott 19, 2013"></div> /* */<span class="meta-category" title="Category"> <i class="icon-tag"></i> <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/archives/category/recensioni/" >Opera</a> </span> <span class="meta-author" title="Author"> <i class="icon-user"></i> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/michele-battistoni/" title="View all posts by Michele Battistoni" rel="author">Michele Battistoni</a></span> </span> <span class="meta-tags" title="Tags"> <i class="icon-tags"></i> <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/andrea-zanin/" rel="tag">Andrea Zanin</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/domenico-colaianni/" rel="tag">domenico colaianni</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/elia-fabbian/" rel="tag">Elia Fabbian</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/fabio-mastrangelo/" rel="tag">Fabio Mastrangelo</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/giacomo-puccini/" rel="tag">Giacomo Puccini</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/giulio-ciabatti/" rel="tag">giulio ciabatti</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/hugo-de-hana/" rel="tag">Hugo de Hana</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/kristian-benedikt/" rel="tag">Kristian Benedikt</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/orfeo-zanetti/" rel="tag">Orfeo Zanetti</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/paolo-battaglia/" rel="tag">Paolo Battaglia</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/teatro-sociale-di-rovigo/" rel="tag">teatro sociale di rovigo</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/tiziana-caruso/" rel="tag">Tiziana Caruso</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/tosca/" rel="tag">Tosca</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/victor-garcia-sierra/" rel="tag">Victor Garcia Sierra</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Andrea Zanin, domenico colaianni, Elia Fabbian, Fabio Mastrangelo, Giacomo Puccini, giulio ciabatti, Hugo de Hana, Kristian Benedikt, Opera lirica, Orfeo Zanetti, Paolo Battaglia, teatro sociale di rovigo, Tiziana Caruso, Tosca, Victor Garcia Sierra"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfi